{"tid":1948988,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"私隱風險 iOS 版 ZOOM 被揭發暗傳使用資料予 Facebook","createTime":"2020-03-29T10:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T11:01:59.000Z","uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3095541b45dee39d502091fc753634e10714619f","tid":1948988,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:51:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-ios-%E7%89%88-zoom-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E6%9A%97%E5%82%B3%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%BA%88-060000459.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA-ios-%25E7%2589%2588-zoom-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%259A%2597%25E5%2582%25B3%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BA%2588-060000459.html&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe1LdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=445500b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-ios-%E7%89%88-zoom-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E6%9A%97%E5%82%B3%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%BA%88-060000459.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/63159_3Y8nnJWCGxvxGLoA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTU1O2g9Mjg2/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/pc3mag.com/5c729f5fe8891aadac379ea77277052a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F63159_3Y8nnJWCGxvxGLoA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTU1O2g9Mjg2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fpc3mag.com%2F5c729f5fe8891aadac379ea77277052a&h=561cd6af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近期，不少人都會使用桌面版及流動版 ZOOM 參與大大小小的會議。但是若大家使用的是 iOS 版 ZOOM，就要小心了。每次我們使用 ZOOM 時，使用的資訊已在不知不覺間傳送予 Facebook。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加拿大媒體 Vice 旗下的科技專欄 Motherboard 發現，當用家使用 iOS 版 ZOOM 時，程式會於用家不知不覺間，傳送多方面的資訊予 Facebook，當中包括使用程式的時間、打開程式的手機型號、用家身處的城市、連接時使用的電訊商及廣告識別碼等。<br />\n<br />\n理論上，按照 Facebook 的規則，若有開發者需要使用 Facebook 的 SDK，他們就需要向用家披露究竟有甚麼資料會傳送至 Facebook，保持透明度。可是，ZOOM 似乎沒有遵守此規則。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 ZOOM 的做法不會對 iOS 用家日常使用帶來影響，但他們隱藏用家傳送資料，這始終是一種不尊重的表現。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ubergizmo.com/2020/03/zoom-ios-app-send-data-facebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ubergizmo.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fzoom-ios-app-send-data-facebook%2F&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe1LdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=e57ff0ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ubergizmo.com/2020/03/zoom-ios-app-send-data-facebook/</a>"},{"pid":"a9f6333d20e5574a18df3b707514c1286fe3d55a","tid":1948988,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"又係豬閪爆格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}